---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro"
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Review the terms and conditions for using Botyoo's Instagram automation platform."
>
  <h1 class="text-foreground mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="mb-4"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 2025-05-08</p>

  <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">
    Welcome to botyoo.com ("Botyoo", "we", "our", or "us"). By accessing or
    using our Instagram automation tool ("Service"), you agree to the following
    Terms of Service ("Terms"). Please read them carefully.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Eligibility</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">To use Botyoo, you must be at least 18 years old and legally able to form a binding contract.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. Use of the Service</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">You agree to:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Provide accurate and complete information during registration</li>
      <li>Use the service in compliance with all applicable laws, regulations, and Meta's platform terms</li>
      <li>Be solely responsible for actions taken using your account</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Prohibited uses include:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Spamming or misusing messaging features</li>
      <li>Violating any third-party rights or platform rules</li>
      <li>Attempting unauthorized access or reverse engineering of the platform</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. Instagram/Meta API Integration</h2>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Our platform relies on official Meta APIs</li>
      <li>Access may be revoked by Meta at any time</li>
      <li>Botyoo is not liable for disruptions caused by changes to Meta's API or policy enforcement</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Subscription & Billing</h2>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Subscriptions are billed in advance and auto-renew unless canceled</li>
      <li>Refunds are issued per our Refund Policy and only under eligible conditions</li>
      <li>You are responsible for canceling your subscription in time to avoid renewal charges</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">5. Termination</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account for any violation of these Terms or misuse of the platform.</p>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">You may also delete your account at any time by contacting support.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">All content, software, and technology used in our platform are owned by or licensed to Botyoo. You may not copy, reproduce, or distribute any part without permission.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Botyoo is provided "as-is." We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Service downtime or disruption</li>
      <li>Loss of data or access</li>
      <li>API limitations or bans</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">8. Indemnification</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Botyoo, its team, and partners from any claim, liability, damage, or loss arising from your use of the platform.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">9. Governing Law</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">These Terms are governed by the laws of Gujarat, India. Disputes shall be resolved through arbitration or courts located in the District Court of Surat.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">Email: <strong class="text-foreground">hevin@botyoo.com</strong></p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
